egory><category>k8s部署实录</category></item><item><title>k8s部署实录-5-RKE节点清理指南：确保节点重新部署的顺利进行</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-5-rke%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 20:05:11 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 20:05:11 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-5-rke%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description>部署集群后出现异常，想重新进行部署，需要在 Kubernetes 集群中清理节点，以确保不影响重新部署。 在本篇博客中，将详细介绍如何使用 RKE（Rancher Kubernetes E</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>RKE</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s部署实录</category></item><item><title>k8s部署实录-4-"sudo echo '192.168.1.218 reg.paas.org' >> /etc/hosts" 报权限拒绝错误</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-4-sudo%E6%8F%90%E6%9D%83echo%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%AC%A6%E4%BC%9A%E6%8A%A5%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 22:05:32 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 22:05:32 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-4-sudo%E6%8F%90%E6%9D%83echo%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%AC%A6%E4%BC%9A%E6%8A%A5%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</guid><description>当你在 Linux 系统中尝试使用 sudo 命令执行操作时，可能会遇到一些令人困惑的问题。其中之一是，为什么在某些情况下，即便使用 sudo 作为超级用户权限，仍然会报告</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Sudo</category><category>Sudo</category><category>k8s部署实录</category></item><item><title>k8s部署实录-3-rke部署集群忽略docker版本校验</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-3-rke%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5docker%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 21:15:10 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 21:15:10 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-3-rke%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5docker%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C/</guid><description>重要 前因： 由于客户现场不给root权限，docker-ce为客户自行安装，版本为24.0.5, 与准备的安装包不兼容（rke版本为v1.2.6</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>RKE</category><category>k8s部署实录</category></item><item><title>k8s部署实录-2-rke指定ssh_key_path配置从而替换默认路径</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-2-rke%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9Assh_key_path%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 20:28:18 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 20:28:18 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-2-rke%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9Assh_key_path%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84/</guid><description>重要 前因： 免密是由客户进行操作，出于安全的考虑，生成ssh-key-gen时选用的加密算法为ed25519, 而非默认的rsa, 从而生成的私钥</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>RKE</category><category>k8s部署实录</category></item><item><title>k8s部署实录-1-web控制台Esc快捷键与vim的热键冲突无法推出编辑模式</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-1-web%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%B0esc%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8Evim%E7%9A%84%E7%83%AD%E9%94%AE%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 19:58:28 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 19:58:28 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-28-k8s%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95-1-web%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%B0esc%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%E4%B8%8Evim%E7%9A%84%E7%83%AD%E9%94%AE%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</guid><description>重要 前因： 客户现场只提供JumpServer的web-client方式连接，root密码甚至是普通用户的密码也不提供。导致只能通过web-c</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Vim</category><category>k8s部署实录</category></item></channel></rss>